Name: Kuroro
Desc: A very timid enemy who will start running when a Construct gets near it. It will be eliminated after bumping into a Construct.

Name: Shark-speare
Desc: A immovable enemy who can kill you if you stay in its sight. Try to eliminate it from behind.

Name: Tai'E
Desc: An enemy who moves along a fixed route. Figure out its moving pattern and make use of the enemy.

Name: Celica
Desc: An innocent ally (?) who accidently got into the puzzle and can be scared off and eliminated just like Kuroro. You can't hurt her.

Name: Roseblade
Desc: After spotting an abnormal occurrence in its sight, the Roseblade will move to where it took place in the next round and stay for a certain number of rounds.
